<typeStatus box="[715,763,1010,1036]" pageId="17" pageNumber="73">type</typeStatus>
locality only, Yangihissar Town in SW 
<collectingRegion box="[1207,1309,1009,1035]" country="China" name="Xinjiang Uygur" pageId="17" pageNumber="73">Xinjiang</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
